<para><anchor id="AEN29"/></para>
<para>Mondo Rescue is a Disaster Recovery Solution which allows you
to effortlessly backup and interactively restore Linux, Windows and
other supported filesystem partitions to/from CD-R/RW media, tape,
NFS, ... and Mindi Linux provides the bootable emergency restore
CD/floppy set which Mondo uses at boot-time.</para>
